'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 3''' is the third issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 2|''Star Wars'' (1977) 2]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"[https://www.comics.org/issue/791786 Hey buddy, can you lend me a...]" {{C|Part 2}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Unknown Worlds of Science Fiction Special Vol 1 1|Threads]]"
*"Behind the Scenes with ''Star Wars Weekly''" {{C|excerpt from ''[[Star Wars Official Collector's Edition]]''}}
*"''Star Wars'' Glossary" {{C|excerpt from ''[[Star Wars Official Collector's Edition]]''}}
*Free gift - a pull-out [[Death Star]] Battleground, to be paired with [[Star Wars Weekly 1|issue 1's]] "[[X-wing starfighter|X-Fighter]]" (sic) and [[Star Wars Weekly 2|issue 2's]] [[TIE fighter|TIE Fighter]] cardboard models.
*Competition to win an "Authentic [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] Helmet" and one of twenty [[Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope Original Soundtrack|''Star Wars'' soundtrack albums.]] In order to enter, readers must answer six simple questions.

